dwstat readme
============

dwstat is a simple informer for dwm (dynamic window manager, see http://dwm.suckless.org).
Right now it can:
* show date in various formats (dd.mm, mm.dd, dd.mm.yyyy, mm.dd.yyyy);
* show time in various formats (hh:mm, hh:mm:ss).


To build dstat:
----
cd <dwstat-dir>/project
make
----

Output binary will be placed at <dwstat-dir>/build/release/dstat.
